Program Goals
Professional Development
We have created several highly-successful programs to help students develop professionally while at MIT.
Community Awareness, Advocacy and Networking
Build personal, professional, and social relationships to enhance your MIT experience
Academic Excellence
Our programs to help students succeed academically at MIT and beyond.
Newsletter
Heads Up! is the biweekly OME newsletter, providing students with information about upcoming OME and MIT events, scholarship- and summer-internship opportunities and other relevant news.
